  "title": "Dental Assistant ( Balestier ) No Need Exp Training Provided #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position:</strong> Dental Assistant (1 position available)<br /><strong>Contract Duration:</strong> 3 months (convertible to permanent)<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,200/month (no experience required) , Experience up $2,700/month<br /><strong>Post-Conversion Salary:</strong> Possible increase of $0 to $200, plus a clinic incentive of approximately 10% of basic salary.</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist the dentist during treatments and procedures.</li><li>Sterilize and prepare dental instruments and equipment.</li><li>Take and develop X-rays (if required).</li><li>Prepare patients and provide post-treatment care instructions.</li><li>Manage patient appointments and maintain records.</li><li>Ensure clinic cleanliness and stock dental supplies.</li><li>Follow safety and infection control protocols.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No prior experience is required.</li></ul><p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p><p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p><p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p><p><strong>Email : </strong><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
